{"tid":1364201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波：近期社會事件對香港國際金融中心聲譽有些影響","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:32:28.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ae449e4c03e08c8d1a89499d042bb2e316efa8e8","tid":1364201,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1470426_1_20190725172616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1470426_1_20190725172616.jpg&h=9496c364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波提到，近期的社會事件對香港國際金融中心地位的聲譽有些影響，一些海外做生意或來港開會的商人，因為近期事件而有憂慮，但並無見到資金大幅外流。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，過去兩個月事件影響一般人信心，對一般市民生活亦有影響，有商戶及餐廳反映生意轉差。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波呼籲大家一起拒絕暴力，「停一停、抖一抖」，重整步伐，繼續向前，又說未來會繼續努力與國際社會更多溝通、交流及解說，讓大家更了解香港情況。"},{"pid":"02481b741f045af162e698fa8ac296612d423ef6","tid":1364201,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470426-20190725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470426-20190725.htm&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6QbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=d937115a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470426-20190725.htm&h=8d23fe84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470426-20190725.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8b3dadc712ae57aad2aed822f7f3abcdbfa6f246","tid":1364201,"uid":120859,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:05:45.000Z","msg":"同你首長講唔該"},{"pid":"2ad02b24184d397e36fe2e099f1f3848c2c841ac","tid":1364201,"uid":35914,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:06:57.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩劏房波，我果四千蚊仲未收到呀"},{"pid":"9da47ec1c1a3e04392d75be27500d4b128709940","tid":1364201,"uid":116967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r